# Optional: enables LLM-assisted natural-language patient replies and semantic
# rubric matching. WITHOUT a key the app runs fully on the deterministic
# engine (keyword/concept matching, verbatim case phrasing).
#
# Never commit a real key. Copy this file to .env.local and fill in.
VITE_LLM_API_KEY=

# Optional model override (default: claude-haiku-4-5 — fast & low-cost, ideal
# for the intent-classification + short-phrasing tasks here). You can also pick
# the model at runtime in the app's "Enable AI" panel.
VITE_LLM_MODEL=
